{"tid":906312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本退將：美國軍事優勢 遠超中國20年","createTime":"2018-11-18T01:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T04:38:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1799f829a217c507d5ee9511692e0ad1c3826c4d","tid":906312,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"日本退將：美國軍事優勢 遠超中國20年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/5982121/article-%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e9%80%80%e5%b0%87%ef%bc%9a%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%bb%8d%e4%ba%8b%e5%84%aa%e5%8b%a2-%e9%81%a0%e8%b6%85%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b20%e5%b9%b4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F5982121%2Farticle-%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e9%2580%2580%25e5%25b0%2587%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%25bb%258d%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%2584%25aa%25e5%258b%25a2-%25e9%2581%25a0%25e8%25b6%2585%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b20%25e5%25b9%25b4%2F&d=xfmZOGnpSnlsLVliURnZafiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=40b9ecdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/5982121/article-%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e9%80%80%e5%b0%87%ef%bc%9a%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%bb%8d%e4%ba%8b%e5%84%aa%e5%8b%a2-%e9%81%a0%e8%b6%85%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b20%e5%b9%b4/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本海上自衛隊前艦隊司令官香田洋二16日在華府表示，美國對中國的軍事優勢，估計至少能維持20年；他並說，絕對不能輸掉台灣，因此美國與日本將不惜代價維護台灣。<br />\n<br />\n華府智庫「哈德遜研究所」16日舉行論壇，探討美中緊張情勢對印太區域的影響，香田洋二（Yoji Koda）、哈德遜研究所海軍研究中心副主任麥格拉斯（Bryan McGrath）等人與會。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防戰略委員會近日向國會提交報告，其中指出美國逐漸喪失軍事優勢，美國未來若與中國或俄羅斯開戰，可能苦戰險勝，或甚至輸掉；該報告寫道，若美國不得不因台灣而與中國開戰，可能面臨「決定性的軍事失敗」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香田洋二16日參與論壇後受訪，被問及若美國漸失軍事優勢，是否可能輸掉台灣？香田洋二回應，「絕不」，台灣是關鍵，因此美日會採取一切措施，不惜代價維護台灣，因為輸掉台灣代表將失去對該區域的所有控制權。<br />\n<br />\n香田洋二接著說，「如果美國領導階層愚蠢至極（很抱歉這麼說美國人），那才可能發生。」他說，若日本意識到可能發生這種狀況，也會立即與美方磋商，雖然美國握有最終決定權，但基本上「失去台灣將是場惡夢」，因此美日將盡最大努力。<br />\n</span><br />\n論壇主持人詢問關於美國是否逐漸喪失軍事優勢，香田洋二表示，他不認為美國的軍事能力下降；雖然中國軍事能力增進，他仍然對於有日本、澳洲等聯盟支持的美國軍事能力非常有信心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香田洋二指出，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國至少在未來20年仍能維持其軍事優勢</span>，所以接下來的20年是關鍵，但就現在而言，根據他的經驗，美軍非常強大，因此他仍有信心。</span>"},{"pid":"8858f70630e26f3b162538b257ece55ef109d0a4","tid":906312,"uid":105366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"臺灣係第一島鏈戰略重地之一。<br />\n為保全太平洋戰略地位不受任何威脅，美日根本就唔會容許蟹軍踏半隻腳上臺灣。"},{"pid":"a27da6661a93c0fabc4fe6e2fe2043a8f8728a74","tid":906312,"uid":316,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8858f70630e26f3b162538b257ece55ef109d0a4","tid":906312,"uid":105366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"臺灣係第一島鏈戰略重地之一。<br />\n為保全太平洋戰略地位不受任何威脅，美日根本就唔會容許蟹軍踏半隻腳上臺灣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:11:33.000Z","msg":"島鏈無左是但一個就可以直出太平洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032ff8ded2fa0f07316f5b62c33b38d7f24b8ac6","tid":906312,"uid":105366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a27da6661a93c0fabc4fe6e2fe2043a8f8728a74","tid":906312,"uid":316,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8858f70630e26f3b162538b257ece55ef109d0a4","tid":906312,"uid":105366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"臺灣係第一島鏈戰略重地之一。<br />\n為保全太平洋戰略地位不受任何威脅，美日根本就唔會容許蟹軍踏半隻腳上臺灣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:11:33.000Z","msg":"島鏈無左是但一個就可以直出太平洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:13:33.000Z","msg":"可以出太平洋就可以威脅美國西岸。<br />\n<br />\n經歷過二戰太平洋戰爭經驗既美國根本唔會容許呢件事發生。"},{"pid":"468835709e8b57e1b727c1f055a82fe2701a957b","tid":906312,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"日本退休將領<br />\n日本退將<br />\n日退"},{"pid":"27ae57e53e85552db3021c2bd219b3b9e557cbeb","tid":906312,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"美國次次都吹自己弱勢，然後買玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f4e0fe6a2e1b81e0f973e1b795e46064119a3f","tid":906312,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:42:24.000Z","msg":"你咁講仲點加軍費呀"},{"pid":"dde42ae0a5b97233a8152939c699ce2795711f25","tid":906312,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468835709e8b57e1b727c1f055a82fe2701a957b","tid":906312,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"日本退休將領<br />\n日本退將<br />\n日退"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"連住尼高登<br />\n連登"},{"pid":"2f37fc98fdf00a8e389f5f278e64f05dba294b63","tid":906312,"uid":158806,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"只唔只?????美國的好奇號日日係火星開緊工，七十年代發射隻航行者一號，去到銀河系邊，仲正常運作，大陸前幾年射上去隻玉兔，係月球都「失聯」，戰鬥機的發動機，仲要用俄國貨，美國的巡航導彈，射程六百公里，誤差只係二米，大陸同類型的導彈，話就話差唔多，但係佢地都承認「未經歷過實戰考驗」"},{"pid":"448af7d68c0215ea9b1b0df077a3c89fb3d9ffeb","tid":906312,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8744e97131deb37c013c9c2a7f1e4ecc0446b1f6","tid":906312,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"美國出報告只會警告唔夠人打<br />\n中國出報告就會話同美國已經分庭伉禮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3c8f01aaaa238524c1d5046168a2266d19bb6e","tid":906312,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:30:58.000Z","msg":"中國國力已經超越美國，要求中國立即出兵，佔領台灣、日本、南韓，建立新東亞共榮圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951aac685f785feab21f36e33def279febbaadf8","tid":906312,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8744e97131deb37c013c9c2a7f1e4ecc0446b1f6","tid":906312,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"美國出報告只會警告唔夠人打<br />\n中國出報告就會話同美國已經分庭伉禮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c948c971cdcac5b31432fcfb61dc5e184fbc359","tid":906312,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8858f70630e26f3b162538b257ece55ef109d0a4","tid":906312,"uid":105366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"臺灣係第一島鏈戰略重地之一。<br />\n為保全太平洋戰略地位不受任何威脅，美日根本就唔會容許蟹軍踏半隻腳上臺灣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:32:38.000Z","msg":"石之瑜觀點：台灣已是美中決戰場，美國必挺民進黨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/898968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/898968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n在台灣問題上，假如華府卯起勁來，迫使北京讓步，那北京的威信勢必將會一落千丈，甚至國內也會出現動盪，美國將可持續稱霸下一個50年。相反的，如果是北京卯起勁來，逼退了華府，就輪到是美國的威信就將一落千丈，北京在未來20年可以立於不敗。除了台灣，他們之間找不到其他議題，還會有這種完全攤牌效果。<br />\n<br />\n如今華府的鷹派眼裡看到的是，中國崛起已經挑戰美國的立國精神，在這個前提下，台灣問題絕對不是什麼地緣戰略、第一島鏈問題，甚至不是台獨自以為的民主自由的問題。雖然民主自由涉及兩國立國精神的對峙，如果北京對台灣根本沒有統一的政策，那台灣的民主自由表現得再腐敗，華府也無所謂。台灣的重要性突然暴增，是兩強爭霸浮上議程以後的事，不是兩強爭霸的原因，而是華府要保衛美國霸權所引發的後果，對華府的重要性尤其飛速提高。"},{"pid":"74e0e8734cda80ed424b8788b7ba6459a9a59f38","tid":906312,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"唔使退休軍官講都知啦下話<br />\n你睇支那連戰機引擎都未搞得掂就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f617507bc1deae6c1db6c8622bcf86fb59c4d71a","tid":906312,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"美國都係為左加軍費先咁講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你而家踢爆佢，美國仲點加軍費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4b3ea244d05edc1b8f48c9661ee6308778f833","tid":906312,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"點止20年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accbef66775b0e9c91754483cf69e0359e126434","tid":906312,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"20年?<br />\n<br />\n40年都未必夠而家個美國打"},{"pid":"a7a62fb0eaff629b355fe28a6f201720ea477c8c","tid":906312,"uid":211046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:50:01.000Z","msg":"我國摺野技術領先美國二百年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5912ff45f917986eda850cd73c8963a656897165","tid":906312,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"好彩支那人唔會知 佢地以為自己天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9850f899391151d3c61abea12e54dc17822f7b6","tid":906312,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"依家科技好似發展慢在,20年算唔算多,質量唔好但個量多期間都煩."},{"pid":"3e92872d4f81b2aba4369016661d414a6d53bbf5","tid":906312,"uid":5006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"講真20年真係算少<br />\n如果只計常規 中共現時戰備連二戰時期既美日都打唔過<br />\n如果計核武 又唔夠冷戰時期既蘇美打<br />\n成日吹整航母 二戰日本都未追到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5f3ba8b7e0c1ceb4e3e247029e840f2fd5650e","tid":906312,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde42ae0a5b97233a8152939c699ce2795711f25","tid":906312,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468835709e8b57e1b727c1f055a82fe2701a957b","tid":906312,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"日本退休將領<br />\n日本退將<br />\n日退"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"連住尼高登<br />\n連登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"高登討論區 -&gt; 高登<br />\n連登討論區 -&gt; 連登"},{"pid":"0e8ae1293b5f83d5d9e01be468f6521eeff1b2ed","tid":906312,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"止